page.title: 18NEWTONMORE CAMANACHD 3
page.content: In one of our photographs you see the most successful shinty team in the recorded history of the game. Their record in Season 1984/85 has never been equalled or bettered. they won the following trophies which can be identified left to right as follows: 1.The Glenmorangie Quaich. 2.The Volante Cup. 3.The MacTavish Cup. 4.The MacGillivray League Cup. 5.The Camanachd Association Challenge Cup. 6.The Weatherseal National League Cup. 7.The Highland Queen Trophy. 8.The MacAulay Cup. 9.The Queen Elizabeth Jubilee Trophy. cont./
